# PWA

## SETUP
@PWA(name, shortName, iconPath, backgroundColor, themeColor, offlinePath) | AppShell implements AppShellConfigurator

## REQUIREMENTS
Icons: 192x192, 512x512 | HTTPS production (mandatory) | Offline: src/main/webapp/offline.html

## ANTIPATTERNS
No HTTPS → fails | Missing icons → no installation
